additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Keep out of reach of children. Read safety instructions. For advice contact a Poisons Information Centre (Phone: Australia 13 11 26; New Zealand: 0800 764 766) or a doctor at once and have product label at hand. If swallowed: do not induce vomiting. If in eyes: holds eyelids apart and flush the eye continuously with running water. Continue flushing until advised to stop by a Poisons Information Centre or doctor, or for at least 15 minutes. If on skin or hair: remove contaminated clothing and flush skin and hair with running water.
